face_recognition_yolov7/
├── detect_faces.py              # Detection + recognition script
├── best.pt                      # Trained YOLOv7 weights
├── known_faces/                 # Folder of labeled reference images
│   ├── alice.jpg
│   └── bob.jpg
├── images/                      # Input images for testing
├── utils/
│   └── face_utils.py            # Optional: helper functions for embeddings
├── requirements.txt             # All dependencies
├── app.py                       # (optional) Flask or Gradio app
└── README.md



